    <briefdescription>
<para>HID axis handler. Declared at sketch scope for each joystick axis. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Self-registers into a static linked list at construction. <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway_1aa8f7b2f81634cf26fff1d4d03b3ec70b" kindref="member">SimGateway::loop()</ref> walks the list and calls OsJoystick.setAxis() when a HID frame with a matching controlId arrives. The 0–65535 unsigned value from <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> is mapped to signed ±32767 internally (value − 32768).</para>
<para>Declare at file scope, not inside functions — C++ constructs file-scope objects before setup() runs, which is required for the linked list to be populated. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
